[packages]
# pytest (or one of its dependencies) is bringing in a version of `atomicwrites` that our mirror
# lacks. I am forcing the most current version that I know exists. Obviously, this has the risk of
# atomicwrites becoming out-of-sync with pytest and its dependencies, but 1.3.0 currently does work.
